      "text": "で、でもほら、アメリカで話し合って\nやっぱり解散やめようって話になったじゃないですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "で、でもほら、アメリカで話し合って\nやっぱり解散やめようって話になったじゃないですか",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そこにはきっと絆が……\nええと……多分、あったんですよね……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "そこにはきっと絆が……\nええと……多分、あったんですよね……？",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_03-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "自分で言っておいて、情けない顔しないで下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "自分で言っておいて、情けない顔しないで下さい",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.4124947229,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_03-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "そもそもあれ、話し合いって言えるのかしら\n向こうから喧嘩売ってきたくせに、勝手にキレてたし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "そもそもあれ、話し合いって言えるのかしら\n向こうから喧嘩売ってきたくせに、勝手にキレてたし",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.4458280562,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_03-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "ろくでもないと思いながら、あの二人と組んで\n気が付いたら、もう何年も経っていたけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "ろくでもないと思いながら、あの二人と組んで\n気が付いたら、もう何年も経っていたけど",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.2124959944,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_09_03-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "そもそも私達らしい歌って、なんなのかしら\n……今更、そんなことを考えるなんてね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "そもそも私達らしい歌って、なんなのかしら\n……今更、そんなことを考えるなんてね",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.9124959944,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
